Minimal signature example (Base64):
```java
PrivateKey pk = Bruce.privateKey(Bruce.keystore("classpath:keystore.p12", "password"), "alice", "password");
EncodingSigner signer = Bruce.signer(pk, "SHA512withRSA", Bruce.Encoding.BASE64);
String sig = signer.sign("Hi Bob!");
```